article.description: — Grant Basile had 20 points as Wright St. rolled past IUPUI 100-72 on Saturday.
article.headline: Basile scores 20 to carry Wright St. past IUPUI 100-72
article.linkText: Basile scores 20 to carry Wright St. past IUPUI 100-72
article.story: INDIANAPOLIS -- — Grant Basile had 20 points as Wright St. rolled past IUPUI 100-72 on Saturday. Tanner Holden had 16 points and seven rebounds for Wright St. (11-4, 9-3 Horizon League). Tim Finke added 16 points and six rebounds. Loudon Love and Jaylon Hall had 13 points. It was the first time this season Wright St. scored at least 100 points. Wright St. totaled 59 points in the second half, a season high for the team. Marcus Burk had 34 points for the Jaguars (3-6, 2-6). Jaylen Minnett added 12 points. Elyjah Goss had 10 rebounds. Wright St. defeated IUPUI 95-65 on Friday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
